{"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Diseq","instances":[],"imports":["Init.Grind.Lemmas","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Types"],"declarations":[{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.lean#L73-L76","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.mkDiseqProof","line":73,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkDiseqProof","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkDiseqProof\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkDiseqProof</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a </span><span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.lean#L65-L71","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.mkDiseqProof?","line":65,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkDiseqProof?","doc":"Returns a proof for `true` if `a` and `b` are known to be disequal.\nSee `getDiseqFor?`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkDiseqProof?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkDiseqProof?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a </span><span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.lean#L42-L63","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.mkDiseqProofUsing","line":42,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkDiseqProofUsing","doc":"Given an equality `eq` of the form `c = d` s.t. `eq` is `False`, and\n`a = b` is congruent to `c = d`, return a proof for `a ≠ b`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.mkDiseqProofUsing\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkDiseqProofUsing</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a </span><span class=\"fn\">b </span><span class=\"fn\">eq</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.lean#L35-L40","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.isDiseq","line":35,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.isDiseq","doc":"Returns `true` if `a` and `b` are known to be disequal.\nSee `getDiseqFor?`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.isDiseq\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">isDiseq</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a </span><span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.lean#L18-L33","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.getDiseqFor?","line":18,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.getDiseqFor?","doc":"Returns `some (c = d)` if\n- `c = d` and `False` are in the same equivalence class, and\n- `a` (`b`) and `c` are in the same equivalence class, and\n- `b` (`a`) and `d` are in the same equivalence class.\nOtherwise return `none`.\n\nRemark `a` and `b` are assumed to have the same type.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Diseq.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.getDiseqFor?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">getDiseqFor?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a </span><span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span></div></div>"}]}